title: didnt get victorious maokai
body: i got the gold border and maokai but the victorious skin is locked for me ( on the alpha client)

replies.body:
We're still rolling those rewards out, so if you sit tight, we'll get the victorious skin out as soon as we can. We're aiming to finish distribution towards the end of the month. 

Let me know if you have any questions. ^.^
It's normal for you to receive some rewards before receiving others. The rewards are still being given out, so just be patient and you will get the skin soon enough.
